hal (0.5.12~git20090114-0maemo1) unstable; urgency=low

  * New downstream git snapshot.
    - Add support for jack video-out and physical insertion notifications.
  * Bump versioned dependencies for udev to 0.125 and dbus to 0.61.
  * Add temporary workaround for RX-51 keymap to match against current
    driver name, and to set a default for all keyboard devices.
    Base on patches by Urpo Pietikäinen and Oliver McFadden.
  * Workaorund a race condition in osspec probes and fdi parsing by merging
    the omap probe into hald.

 -- Guillem Jover <guillem.jover@nokia.com>  Thu, 15 Jan 2009 16:40:42 +0200

