hal (0.5.12~git20081105-0maemo1) unstable; urgency=low

  * New downstream git snapshot.
    - Add jack insertion support.
    - Fix mmc slot_name values. The kernel started prefixing them with
      "slot:", which gets now normalized by hal.
    - Drop mtd devices, they are not actually useful.
    - Refactor and fix testing shell scripts to not depend on hal-info.
  * Use binary:Version instead of deprecated Source-Version substvar.

