    - Scan the mmc bus, to trigger volume detection after the class scan.
      Thanks to Ismo Laitinen.
  * Fix harmless lintian *warning* about an actual shell script having the
    exec bits set, but missing a shebang. This was causing rejects at
    integration time, *sigh*.

