    - Add mtd character device support.
    - Add ALS addon. Thanks to Semi Malinen.
  * Install the udev rules file directly under /etc/udev/rules.d/ instead of
    symlinking from the parent directory. (Fixes: NB#53994)
  * Conditionally build the HAL spec if building binary independent packages,
    by including xmlto and libxml2-utils to the Build-Depends-Indep.

